Sure. Just run some hose into a gas can:

http://homepage.mac.com/ratwell/.Pictures/78%20Camper/03-Custom%20Fuel%20Tank.jpg

>also if i need
>to change the fuel lines i would like to find out some of your opinions on
>where to find the best.

Continental 7x3mm high pressure hose from the online vendors. N 020 281 1.
Get the smooth jacket, not the braided stuff.

>i want all of them from the pickup tube all the
>way to the injectors.   thank you guys in advance.

You have to buy bulk hose and cut it yourself:

